<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA79">
<l>uṇṇāṭṭut tēcaṉṟē yūḻviṉaiyai yañcumē</l>
<l>viṇṇāṭṭai yoṉṟāka meccumē maṇṇāṭṭi</l>
<l>lārāki yevviḻiviṟ ṟāṉālu māḻiyaṅkaip</l>
<l>pērāyaṟ kāḷām piṟappu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will it not be a light in the inner land, will it fear maturing Karma,</l>
<l>will it admire the heavenly land as one – the birth that is as a servant</l>
<l>to the great cowherd with the discus in [his] palm, </l>
<l>whoever it may be [and] however lowly.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
